    "description": "Discipline: None\nSkill: Endurance against Resolve\nType: Normal\nQi: 24\n\nYou concentrate with your body and mind, flowing Qi energy from your body to create a force field around anyone with demonic essence. You then make a seal to trap them with your life energy. Roll Endurance against the Resolve against any targets with negative Karma. If you keep them in place for five minutes and succeed, they are trapped by the force field for a period of time determined by the seal. The strength of the seal is set by your life energy and by their negative Karma rating. For every point of Hardiness you imbue into the seal and for every point of negative Karma they have, it traps them for 1 decade. This Hardiness is restored to your when the seal is broken. This takes five minutes to perform.",
